= Ratpack Sample Project

== Description

This is sample application used to demo Geb Testing, and not as a reference for how to use Ratpack.

The application is however a working example o how to use Gorm in Ratpack, if that is what you need,
based in large parts by the book "Learning Ratpack" by Dan Woods.

== Starting the application

You can start the basic app with

 ./gradlew run

== Testing the application

 ./gradlew check
